posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 58', 'OR Text', '58', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'This is a 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1107 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Join the apartment life at 8181 Med Center, a Houston home near the Downtown area.', 'With studio, one-, two-, and three-bedroom apartments available, all luxuriantly finished, 8181 is ready to lease you your preferred floor plan today.', 'Shared spaces account for daily needs and priorities at every stage, as our community amenities were procured for exercise on your schedule, evening cookouts, personal convenience, poolside recreation, and movie screenings, as well.', 'Features:', "Full-size Washer and Dryer Connections, Undermount Kitchen Sink*, USB Port in Kitchen*, Two-Inch Wood-Style Blinds*, Subway Tile Backsplash, Plush Bedroom Carpeting*, Linen Closets, GE Stainless-steel Appliances Including Dishwasher*, Digital Thermostats*, Central Heating and Air, Kitchen Faucet with Sprayer*, Ceilings Fans*, Lighted Ceiling Fans*, Breakfast Bar*, Brushed Nickel Cabinet Hardware*, Upgraded Lighting Fixtures*, Kitchen Pantry, Designer-selected Paint Finishings*, Walk-In Closets, Storage Closet, Granite Countertops*, Private Patio/Balcony, Ideal Location in the Heart of The Medical Center, Wood-style Flooring*, Open-Concept Chef's Kitchen", '*Restrictions apply.', 'See Sales Associate for details.', 'Community Amenities:', 'Sundeck with Gazebo, Clothes Care Center, Covered Parking/Garages Available, Gated Access Community, 24/7 Emergency Maintenance Services, MetroRail', 'Located Across from the Leasing Center, Barbecue and Picnic Areas, Extra Storage Available, State-of-the-Art-24-Hour Fitness Center, Wi-Fi in Clubhouse and Pool Area, Two Swimming Pools and a Wading Pool, Movie Theater, Resident Business Center', 'Pet Policy', 'We Love Pets!', 'Income Requirements:', 'Three times the monthly rent', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'Xk710CGoaP']
